{"tid":2038977,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"撐不住！波音本週將公布美國大規模裁員","createTime":"2020-05-27T20:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T00:55:12.000Z","uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"38f949db9b9250ca3227a82229ce53a499b1e059","tid":2038977,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T20:25:30.000Z","msg":"撐不住！波音本週將公布美國大規模裁員<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4482221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cnyes.com%2Fnews%2Fid%2F4482221&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32QweZXAU%2BhIfMqCJmwSRnXM%3D&h=f4e60702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4482221</a><br />\n<br />\n美國波音公司 (BA-US) 傳出要在美國進行大規模裁員的消息，預估在本週就會正式公布。<br />\n<br />\n根據《路透社》5 月 26 日報導，在新冠肺炎 (COVID-19) 疫情影響下，全球的航空產業受到重創。美國波音公司也發布消息，將對全球 16 萬名員工進行 10% 的人事精簡。<br />\n<br />\nSPEEA (Society of Professional Engineering Employees in Aerospace) 在週二 (26 日) 向《路透社》表示，說波音公司預告在本月 29 日的時候會通知他們進行裁員。在目前有 1.76 萬名的波音員工加入 SPEEA。<br />\n<br />\n但是在截稿前，波音公司未對這項消息發表評論。"},{"pid":"e860fb934e245b8ca0a8e7433bd792e59cfdad67","tid":2038977,"uid":195827,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T20:30:13.000Z","msg":"裁員 = cut cost -&gt; 大升"},{"pid":"24de65acc2145561204ec4684d3b4573455606b0","tid":2038977,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T20:40:47.000Z","msg":"其實有邊間掂？"},{"pid":"ac5b5ac24a569fdefd1b6e9b7027cc9289516ae9","tid":2038977,"uid":77134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24de65acc2145561204ec4684d3b4573455606b0","tid":2038977,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T20:40:47.000Z","msg":"其實有邊間掂？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T20:56:24.000Z","msg":"Airbus"},{"pid":"a59beef6ed76788c2fa3997464f6effaeab94f0e","tid":2038977,"uid":22243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"24de65acc2145561204ec4684d3b4573455606b0","tid":2038977,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score